00:53:00,000 --> 00:53:01,000
Di xelat di xwe bide.
 
Give the gift yourself.

768
00:53:01,000 --> 00:53:03,000
Migo keke xelat ne li cem min e. Nere ser mesrehe.
 
I said brother the gift is not with me. Don't go on stage.

769
00:53:03,000 --> 00:53:07,000
Migo xelat ne li cem min e, nede min, derbasî cem qutîyê
salonek e, te.. erê taleşo baş e.
 
I said the gift is not with me, don't give it to me, go to
the hall box, you.. yes it's good.

770
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:08,000
Yanî vê mewqifê min...
 
I mean this situation of mine...

771
00:53:08,000 --> 00:53:09,000
Însan di xecil e.
 
A person is embarrassed.

772
00:53:09,000 --> 00:53:13,000
Xecil e, û ken e.. min xwe di stranê xwe de wunda kir yanî..
 
Embarrassed, and funny.. I lost myself in my song, I mean..

773
00:53:13,000 --> 00:53:17,000
Ba'dêkî tiştek dihat bîra min yanî, ser mesrehem, ewe hatî
cem min yeke xelatek bi min de yanî.
 
After a while something came to my mind, I mean, on stage,
that one came to me giving me a gift, I mean.

774
00:53:17,000 --> 00:53:18,000
Te dît ku çawa ye?
 
Did you see how it is?

775
00:53:18,000 --> 00:53:19,000
Belê.
 
Yes.

776
00:53:19,000 --> 00:53:21,000
Erê weleh bi Xwedê. Em miletek afûne.
 
Yes by God. We are a forgiving nation.

777
00:53:21,000 --> 00:53:23,000
Em pir însanekî basît ne, em Efrînî.
 
We are very simple people, we Afrinians.

778
00:53:23,000 --> 00:53:25,000
Erê. Erê. Dilê me pak e, em erê...
 
Yes. Yes. Our hearts are pure, we yes...

779
00:53:25,000 --> 00:53:26,000
Mamoste Hîmo.
 
Teacher Himo.

780
00:53:26,000 --> 00:53:28,000
Spasiya te dikim, ez pir kêfxweş me!
 
I thank you, I am very happy!

781
00:53:28,000 --> 00:53:29,000
Spas ji tera jî.
 
Thank you too.

782
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:33,000
Te bi mêvandariya qenala Hatim Efrîn, cara yekemîn te ser
qenala derket. Daxwaz dikim dengekî bike.
 
Being a guest on Hatim Efrîn channel, the first time you
appeared on the channel. I request you to make a sound.

783
00:53:33,000 --> 00:53:34,000
Erê.
 
Yes.

784
00:53:34,000 --> 00:53:36,000
Me daxwaz in em tiştan bi hev ra...
 
We requested things together...

785
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:40,000
...Bi dest axiftinek me hebî, bi bav û kalan da gotibû,
"destê ki çepka nakeve".
 
...We had a saying from our ancestors, "one hand cannot
clap".

786
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:41,000
Na.
 
No.

787
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:42,000
Em gişt yek hevin da em karibin dinya...
 
We are all one together so we can...

788
00:53:42,000 --> 00:53:42,000
Em spasiya kekê welo dikin. Îro her hevin.
 
Yes.

789
00:53:42,000 --> 00:53:45,000
Em spasiya kekê welo dikin. Îro her hevin.
 
We thank brother Welo. They are always together today.

790
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:46,000
Spas welleh.
 
Thanks by God.

791
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:50,000
Û înşelleh pir tiştên xweş em ê bi hev ra çêkin. Kekê Elî
Çavîş, ji gundê Maratê ye...
 
And hopefully we will make many nice things together.
Brother Ali Chavish, from Marate village...

792
00:53:50,000 --> 00:53:52,000
...Silav û hurmet ji malbata Çavîş heta dawîyê ra.
 
...Greetings and respect to the Chavish family to the end.

793
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:53,000
Ser serê min, em bi xêr hatin.
 
On my head, welcome.

794
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:56,000
Înşelleh vîdyoyên xweş em ê pir bidin em ê bi hev ra çêkin.
 
Hopefully we will give many nice videos, we will make them
together.

795
00:53:56,000 --> 00:53:57,000
Kekê Heme.
 
Brother Heme.

796
00:53:57,000 --> 00:53:58,000
Ne hemî.
 
Not all.

797
00:53:58,000 --> 00:54:00,000
Heme, Heme.
 
Heme, Heme.

798
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:02,000
Heme me, Heme me hey.
 
I am Heme, I am Heme, hey.

799
00:54:02,000 --> 00:54:04,000
Ya kekê Heme, em spasiya te dikin.
 
Oh brother Heme, we thank you.

800
00:54:04,000 --> 00:54:07,000
Xwedê emrekî dirêj bide te, destê we sax bin hîn her hebin.
 
May God give you a long life, bless your hands, may you
always exist.

801
00:54:07,000 --> 00:54:11,000
Gelî temaşevanan, me hîş hişt em spasiya we dikin, bi me ra
bin ta dawiya vîdyo.
 
Dear viewers, we kept you in mind, we thank you, be with us
until the end of the video.

802
00:54:11,000 --> 00:54:14,000
Em spasiya musawirê me, Hesen Celhût...
 
We thank our cameraman, Hasan Jalhout...

803
00:54:14,000 --> 00:54:17,000
Groupa Medya. Em spasiya gena dikin.
 
Media Group. We thank the group.

804
00:54:17,000 --> 00:54:18,000
Spasiya kekê Şiyarî Maratê.
 
Thanks to brother Shiyar from Marate.

805
00:54:18,000 --> 00:54:20,000
Bavê ciwan.
 
Father of youths.

806
00:54:20,000 --> 00:54:22,000
Spasiya şebabê ji me ra hazir bîn e.
 
Thanks to the youth who were present for us.

807
00:54:22,000 --> 00:54:24,000
Em spasiya wan jî dikin.
 
We thank them too.

808
00:54:24,000 --> 00:54:27,000
Em spasiya we dikin, bi me re bîn heta dawîyê vîdyo.
 
We thank you, be with us until the end of the video.

809
00:54:27,000 --> 00:54:30,000
Ku ez daxwazim hûn ji me re yazmîş kin, car din em kê ji we
ra bînin ser ekranê?
 
If I ask you to write to us, who else should we bring to the
screen for you?

810
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:35,000
Yanî hunermendî hene, em tiştan jê re pirsin, em bi hev ra
bi dengekî girtin e.
 
I mean there are artists, we will ask them things, we
recorded together with a sound.

811
00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:40,000
Saetên we xweş, û bîr mekin qenala Hatim Efrîn da'm bikin.
 
Have a good time, and don't forget to support Hatim Afrin
channel.

